  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Right2Change, is a justice for children intervention that deploys a community-based structured diversion approach. It prevents illegal detention for children in conflict with the law aged 12 to 17 while promoting their rehabilitation at community level. Right2Change brings together legal aid, youth training, employment and microfinance service providers to deliver a holistic &#x2018;structured diversion&#x2019; package of care.</narrative>
  </description>
